Because the tar.gz file contains an un-named folder "." the tar type extractor is not able to extract the contents of the folder. If the folder is named there is no problem.

<details><summary>File: composer.json</summary>

```json
    "require": {
        "ec-europa/platform_dev": "~2.4.0"
    },
    "repositories": [
        {
            "type": "package",
            "package": {
